		<li><a href="http://www.cqc.org.uk/about-us/how-we-are-run/board-meetings">Board meetings</a></li>
		<li><a href="http://www.cqc.org.uk/news/our-media-office/our-media-office">Meet the media team</a></li>
	</ul>
	<h3>Our news on social media</h3>
	<ul class="social">
		<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/CareQualityCommission" title="CQC on Facebook"><img alt="CQC on Facebook" height="25" src="http://www.cqc.org.uk/sites/default/files/25x25_facebook.png" width="25"></a></li>
